```plantuml
@startuml chrispiro_deploy_plotly_app_on_gcp

actor Developer

participant "Jupyter Notebook" as JN
participant "Dash App" as DA
participant "GCP App Engine" as GAE
participant "BigQuery" as BQ
participant "Cloud Storage" as CS
participant "GCP Virtual Private Cloud" as VPC

Developer -> JN: Experiment with Plotly charts
JN -> DA: Add chart code to dash_app.py
Developer -> DA: Define app layout and load_data.py logic

Developer -> GAE: Deploy using app.yaml
GAE -> DA: Launch Dash app
DA -> BQ: Request data
DA -> CS: Request data
BQ --> DA: Return data
CS --> DA: Return data

DA -> DA: Create Plotly charts
DA -> Developer: Provide interactive UI

note over GAE, VPC
Communicate within GCP services
end note

@enduml
```